# ======================================================================
# OPTIONAL — Workshops and Plans (prices) from a Google Sheet.
# The site runs WITHOUT this (it shows built-in fallback workshops),
# so you can leave these blank for local testing. Reviews need NOTHING
# here — they are curated in lib/reviews.ts (no API key, no API calls).
#
# To make Workshops live later:
# 1. Sheet with tabs named exactly: Workshops and Plans  (columns in README.md).
# 2. Share: "Anyone with the link -> Viewer".
# 3. Google Cloud Console -> enable "Google Sheets API" -> create an API key.
# 4. Spreadsheet id is in the URL:
#    https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/THIS_IS_THE_ID/edit
# ======================================================================
SHEET_ID=
GOOGLE_SHEETS_API_KEY=
SHEET_WORKSHOPS_RANGE=Workshops!A2:J
SHEET_PLANS_RANGE=Plans!A2:I
SHEET_KIDS_RANGE=Kids!A2:H
SHEET_TESTIMONIALS_RANGE=Testimonials!A2:F
SHEET_CONTACT_RANGE=Contact!A2:H
